OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FWater bills expected to    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Frise, says regulator       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Water bills are likely to rise in 2025 
OL,6, to cover the cost of improving         
OL,7, suppliers' services, the boss of       
OL,8, regulator Ofwat has said.              
OL,10,FIt comes after the biggest providers   
OL,11,Fhave been severely criticised for their
OL,12,Frecords on sewage spills and plugging  
OL,13,Fleaks.                                 
OL,15,FMany are also heavily in debt, with    
OL,16,FThames Water currently at risk of being
OL,17,Ftaken over by the government.          
OL,19,FOfwat boss David Black denied it had   
OL,20,Ffailed to regulate the industry well.  
